<p>If can't rely on the process name like python scripts which will always have python.exe as process name. If found this method very handy</p>

<pre><code>import psutil
psutil.pid_exists(pid)
</code></pre>

<p>check docs for further info
<a href="http://psutil.readthedocs.io/en/latest/#psutil.pid_exists" rel="nofollow noreferrer">http://psutil.readthedocs.io/en/latest/#psutil.pid_exists</a></p>
